</div>
<div class="GSummary21 Summary4">
<i class="Summary5 fa fa-book"></i>
<a class="Summary6" href="#installation-de-font-awesome_fichier-archive">Fichier archive</a>
</div>
</div><br><h2 class="GTitle1 Title1">
<a class="Title2" id="installation-de-font-awesome_page-de-telechargement" href="#installation-de-font-awesome-v6-4-0">Page de téléchargement</a>
</h2><br><a class="GLink3 Link4" style=" color: lime;" href="https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome" target="_blank">https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome</a><br><br><h2 class="GTitle1 Title1">
